      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:8:54:4",
      "text": [
        " سَمِعْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) يَقُولُ إِنَّهُ لَيُعْجِبُنِي الْخَلُوقُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from a man, from Muhammad Bin Al Fayz who said, ",
          "‘I heard Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> saying: ‘I<sup>asws</sup> love <span class=\"iTxt\">Al-Khalouq</span>’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from a man from Muhammad ibn al-Fayd who has said the following: “I once heard abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, saying, ‘I like al-Khuluq.”’ "
        ]
      }
